<heading id="85358192FFAD1223FF6CFCFE25BEFCFE" bold="true" box="[136,718,842,869]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" reason="1">
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FF6CFCFE25BEFCFE" bold="true" box="[136,718,842,869]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">
Typification of the name 
<taxonomicName id="19C24D7DFFAD1223FE56FCFE25BEFCFE" authorityName="v. Poellnitz" authorityYear="2022" box="[434,718,842,869]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="blossfeldiana">
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FE56FCFE25BEFCFE" bold="true" box="[434,718,842,869]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">Kalanchoe blossfeldiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="96D86575FFAD1223FF6CFC262494FAA3" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="DE7D36FEFFAD1223FF6CFC26254CFB1F" blockId="3.[136,1452,914,2093]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">
The name 
<taxonomicName id="19C24D7DFFAD1223FF1BFC2726C4FC37" authorityName="v. Poellnitz" authorityYear="2022" box="[255,436,914,940]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="blossfeldiana">
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FF1BFC2726C4FC37" box="[255,436,914,940]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">K. blossfeldiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was effectively typified when 
<bibRefCitation id="BA534B0FFFAD1223FCEBFC2723F8FC36" author="Van Voorst, A. &amp; Arends, J. C." box="[783,1160,914,941]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" pagination="573 - 584" refId="ref5136" refString="Van Voorst, A. &amp; Arends, J. C. (1982) The origin and chromosome numbers of cultivars of Kalanchoe blossfeldiana Von Poelln.: their history and evolution. Euphytica 31 (3): 573 - 584." type="journal article" year="1982">Van Voorst &amp; Arends (1982: 575)</bibRefCitation>
stated: “In conclusion we wish to assign this number [Perrier 17833] as the 
<typeStatus id="0179885CFFAD1223FD22FC02245DFC4B" box="[710,813,950,976]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">lectotype</typeStatus>
…”. 
<bibRefCitation id="BA534B0FFFAD1223FC8AFC032380FC4A" author="Van Voorst, A. &amp; Arends, J. C." box="[878,1264,950,977]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" pagination="573 - 584" refId="ref5136" refString="Van Voorst, A. &amp; Arends, J. C. (1982) The origin and chromosome numbers of cultivars of Kalanchoe blossfeldiana Von Poelln.: their history and evolution. Euphytica 31 (3): 573 - 584." type="journal article" year="1982">Van Voorst &amp; Arends (1982: 575)</bibRefCitation>
cited the wrong number, i.e., “178 
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FEB4FC6E262EFC6F" bold="true" box="[336,350,986,1012]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">3</emphasis>
3”—it should have been 178 
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FD79FC6E25DBFC6F" bold="true" box="[669,683,986,1012]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">8</emphasis>
3; this error in the specimen number also appears on page 574 of 
<bibRefCitation id="BA534B0FFFAD1223FA64FC6F26ECFB83" author="Van Voorst, A. &amp; Arends, J. C." pageId="3" pageNumber="107" pagination="573 - 584" refId="ref5136" refString="Van Voorst, A. &amp; Arends, J. C. (1982) The origin and chromosome numbers of cultivars of Kalanchoe blossfeldiana Von Poelln.: their history and evolution. Euphytica 31 (3): 573 - 584." type="journal article" year="1982">Van Voorst &amp; Arends (1982)</bibRefCitation>
. No Perrier de la Bâthie specimen with the number 17833 could be located at Herb. P or in a repository elsewhere. However, the typographic error of 
<bibRefCitation id="BA534B0FFFAD1223FCF9FB9723EAFBA6" author="Van Voorst, A. &amp; Arends, J. C." box="[797,1178,1058,1085]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" pagination="573 - 584" refId="ref5136" refString="Van Voorst, A. &amp; Arends, J. C. (1982) The origin and chromosome numbers of cultivars of Kalanchoe blossfeldiana Von Poelln.: their history and evolution. Euphytica 31 (3): 573 - 584." type="journal article" year="1982">Van Voorst &amp; Arends (1982: 575)</bibRefCitation>
is to be corrected under 
<bibRefCitation id="BA534B0FFFAD1223FF6CFBF2261EFBFB" author="Turland, N. J. &amp; Wiersema, J. H. &amp; Barrie, F. R. &amp; Greuter, W. &amp; Hawksworth, D. L. &amp; Herendeen, P. S. &amp; Knapp, S. &amp; Kusber, W. - H. &amp; Li, D. - Z. &amp; Marhold, K. &amp; May, T. W. &amp; McNeill, J. &amp; Monro, A. M. &amp; Prado, J. &amp; Price, M. J. &amp; Smith, G. F." box="[136,366,1094,1121]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" refId="ref4970" refString="Turland, N. J., Wiersema, J. H., Barrie, F. R., Greuter, W., Hawksworth, D. L., Herendeen, P. S., Knapp, S., Kusber, W. - H., Li, D. - Z., Marhold, K., May, T. W., McNeill, J., Monro, A. M., Prado, J., Price, M. J. &amp; Smith, G. F. (2018) International Code of Nomenclature for algae, fungi, and plants (Shenzhen Code) adopted by the Nineteenth International Botanical Congress Shenzhen, China, July 2017. Koeltz Botanical Books, Glashutten. [Regnum Vegetabile 159], 254 pp. [https: // www. iapt-taxon. org / nomen / main. php]" type="book" year="2018">
Turland 
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FF0CFBF3266AFBFB" box="[232,282,1094,1120]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">et al</emphasis>
. (2018
</bibRefCitation>
: Art. 
<specimenCount id="C8C4FD77FFAD1223FE49FBF22699FBFA" box="[429,489,1094,1121]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" type="generic">9 Ex.</specimenCount>
3), which relates to errors in citation of a 
<typeStatus id="0179885CFFAD1223FC2EFBF2235FFBFB" box="[970,1071,1094,1120]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">holotype</typeStatus>
, which 
<bibRefCitation id="BA534B0FFFAD1223FB63FBF322DBFBFA" author="Von Poellnitz &amp; L. A" box="[1159,1451,1094,1121]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" pagination="159 - 160" refId="ref5180" refString="Von Poellnitz, [J.] K. [L. A.]. (1934) XV. Kalanchoe Blossfeldiana. Repertorium specierum novarum regni vegetabilis. Centralblatt fur Sammlung und Veroffentlichung von Einzeldiagnosen neuer Pflanzen 35: 159 - 160. [https: // bibdigital. rjb. csic. es / ing / Libro. php? Libro = 6015]" type="journal article" year="1934">Von Poellnitz (1934: 159)</bibRefCitation>
intended for “H. Perrier de la Bâthie!”.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="DE7D36FEFFAD1223FF59FB3A23F5FB56" blockId="3.[136,1452,914,2093]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">
<materialsCitation id="6EAA3CA3FFAD1223FF59FB3A23F2FB56" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3802850301" collectorName="Perrier de la Bathie. The" country="Madagascar" location="Perrier" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" specimenCount="1">
<bibRefCitation id="BA534B0FFFAD1223FF59FB3A26CBFB33" author="Descoings, B." box="[189,443,1166,1192]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" pagination="143 - 181" refId="ref3596" refString="Descoings, B. (2003) Kalanchoe. In: U. Eggli (Ed.) Illustrated handbook of succulent plants: Crassulaceae. Springer-Verlag, Berlin &amp; Heidelberg, pp. 143 - 181." type="book chapter" year="2003">Descoings (2003: 148)</bibRefCitation>
cited “ 
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FDE8FB3A256FFB33" bold="true" box="[524,543,1166,1192]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">T</emphasis>
: 
<collectingCountry id="A6D5766EFFAD1223FDC9FB3A25C4FB33" box="[557,692,1166,1192]" name="Madagascar" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
(
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FD20FB3B2466FB33" box="[708,790,1167,1192]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">
<location id="DB1D6025FFAD1223FD20FB3B2466FB33" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:566B87E8FFAD1223FF6CFCFE25E0F7B7:DB1D6025FFAD1223FD20FB3B2466FB33" box="[708,790,1167,1192]" country="Madagascar" name="Perrier" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">Perrier</location>
</emphasis>
17883 [P])” and referenced the correct gathering of 
<collectorName id="73375328FFAD1223FABBFB3A2637FB57" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">Perrier de la Bâthie. The</collectorName>
abbreviation “ 
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FE09FB062570FB57" bold="true" box="[493,512,1202,1228]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">T</emphasis>
” is defined as “(nomenclatural) 
<typeStatus id="0179885CFFAD1223FC89FB0624D0FB57" box="[877,928,1202,1228]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">type</typeStatus>
” in 
<bibRefCitation id="BA534B0FFFAD1223FC29FB062326FB57" author="Eggli, U." box="[973,1110,1202,1228]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" refId="ref3634" refString="Eggli, U. (Ed.) (2003) Illustrated handbook of succulent plants: Crassulaceae. Springer-Verlag, Berlin &amp; Heidelberg, 458 pp + plates I - XLVIII." type="book" year="2003">Eggli (2003</bibRefCitation>
: X)
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="DE7D36FEFFAD1223FF59FB632494FAA3" blockId="3.[136,1452,914,2093]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">
In a second-step lectotypification the lectotypification of 
<bibRefCitation id="BA534B0FFFAD1223FCA6FB6323CDFB6A" author="Van Voorst, A. &amp; Arends, J. C." box="[834,1213,1238,1265]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" pagination="573 - 584" refId="ref5136" refString="Van Voorst, A. &amp; Arends, J. C. (1982) The origin and chromosome numbers of cultivars of Kalanchoe blossfeldiana Von Poelln.: their history and evolution. Euphytica 31 (3): 573 - 584." type="journal article" year="1982">Van Voorst &amp; Arends (1982: 575)</bibRefCitation>
is narrowed down to the 
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FF55FB4F26AEFA8F" box="[177,478,1274,1300]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">Perrier de la Bâthie 17883</emphasis>
specimen with the barcode P00374114. This is the specimen that 
<bibRefCitation id="BA534B0FFFAD1223FB5AFB4F267CFAA2" author="Van Voorst, A. &amp; Arends, J. C." pageId="3" pageNumber="107" pagination="573 - 584" refId="ref5136" refString="Van Voorst, A. &amp; Arends, J. C. (1982) The origin and chromosome numbers of cultivars of Kalanchoe blossfeldiana Von Poelln.: their history and evolution. Euphytica 31 (3): 573 - 584." type="journal article" year="1982">Van Voorst &amp; Arends (1982: 575)</bibRefCitation>
likely intended as 
<typeStatus id="0179885CFFAD1223FE3BFAAA2539FAA3" box="[479,585,1310,1336]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">lectotype</typeStatus>
, but cited with the incorrect number.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="96D86575FFAD1223FF59FAF626CCF93A" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="DE7D36FEFFAD1223FF59FAF626ADFA1B" blockId="3.[136,1452,914,2093]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">
The typification of the name 
<taxonomicName id="19C24D7DFFAD1223FDEFFAF725B2FAC7" authorityName="v. Poellnitz" authorityYear="2022" box="[523,706,1346,1372]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="blossfeldiana">
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FDEFFAF725B2FAC7" box="[523,706,1346,1372]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">K. blossfeldiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
resolves as follows, with the original French text in Perrier de la Bâthie translated into English:
</paragraph>
