<subSubSection id="96D86575FFAD1223FF59F88E25E0F7B7" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="DE7D36FEFFAD1223FF59F88E2314F87E" blockId="3.[136,1452,914,2093]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FF59F88E2582F8CF" bold="true" box="[189,754,1850,1876]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">Notes on the not validly published designations</emphasis>
:—The two ‘names’: (1) 
<taxonomicName id="19C24D7DFFAD1223FBE9F88F23E1F8CF" box="[1037,1169,1851,1876]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="coccinea">
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FBE9F88F23E1F8CF" box="[1037,1169,1851,1876]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">K. coccinea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, published at the rank of species, and (2) 
<taxonomicName id="19C24D7DFFAD1223FEDAF8EB25FFF8E3" box="[318,655,1886,1913]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="coccinea" variety="blossfeldiana">
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FEDAF8EB26B3F8E3" box="[318,451,1887,1912]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">K. coccinea</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FE1EF8EA25FFF8E3" box="[506,655,1886,1912]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">blossfeldiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, published at the rank of variety, represent two different ‘names’ based on the same 
<typeStatus id="0179885CFFAD1223FEF3F837263AF806" box="[279,330,1923,1949]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">type</typeStatus>
, i.e., that of 
<taxonomicName id="19C24D7DFFAD1223FE33F8372460F807" authorityName="Perrier de la Bathie" authorityYear="1928" box="[471,784,1922,1949]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="globulifera" variety="coccinea">
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FE33F8372504F807" box="[471,628,1922,1948]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">K. globulifera</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FD49F8372460F807" box="[685,784,1923,1948]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">coccinea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, which were accepted simultaneously as alternatives in the same publication by Boiteau in 
<bibRefCitation id="BA534B0FFFAD1223FE09F81224D6F85B" author="Boiteau, P. &amp; Allorge-Boiteau, L." box="[493,934,1958,1985]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" refId="ref3218" refString="Boiteau, P. &amp; Allorge-Boiteau, L. (1995) Kalanchoe (Crassulacees) de Madagascar. Systematique, Ecophysiologie et Phytochimie. ICSN, CNRS, 91198 Gif-sur-Yvette, Editions Karthala, Paris, 252 pp." type="book" year="1995">Boiteau &amp; Allorge-Boiteau (1995: 188)</bibRefCitation>
and by Boiteau in 
<bibRefCitation id="BA534B0FFFAD1223FB98F812267DF87F" author="Boiteau, P. &amp; Allorge-Boiteau, L." pageId="3" pageNumber="107" refId="ref3218" refString="Boiteau, P. &amp; Allorge-Boiteau, L. (1995) Kalanchoe (Crassulacees) de Madagascar. Systematique, Ecophysiologie et Phytochimie. ICSN, CNRS, 91198 Gif-sur-Yvette, Editions Karthala, Paris, 252 pp." type="book" year="1995">Boiteau &amp; Allorge-Boiteau (1995: 190)</bibRefCitation>
, respectively. Neither was validly published (
<bibRefCitation id="BA534B0FFFAD1223FCEFF87E2496F87F" author="Turland, N. J. &amp; Wiersema, J. H. &amp; Barrie, F. R. &amp; Greuter, W. &amp; Hawksworth, D. L. &amp; Herendeen, P. S. &amp; Knapp, S. &amp; Kusber, W. - H. &amp; Li, D. - Z. &amp; Marhold, K. &amp; May, T. W. &amp; McNeill, J. &amp; Monro, A. M. &amp; Prado, J. &amp; Price, M. J. &amp; Smith, G. F." box="[779,998,1994,2021]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" refId="ref4970" refString="Turland, N. J., Wiersema, J. H., Barrie, F. R., Greuter, W., Hawksworth, D. L., Herendeen, P. S., Knapp, S., Kusber, W. - H., Li, D. - Z., Marhold, K., May, T. W., McNeill, J., Monro, A. M., Prado, J., Price, M. J. &amp; Smith, G. F. (2018) International Code of Nomenclature for algae, fungi, and plants (Shenzhen Code) adopted by the Nineteenth International Botanical Congress Shenzhen, China, July 2017. Koeltz Botanical Books, Glashutten. [Regnum Vegetabile 159], 254 pp. [https: // www. iapt-taxon. org / nomen / main. php]" type="book" year="2018">
Turland 
<emphasis id="ECB6EAECFFAD1223FC8FF87F24ECF87F" box="[875,924,1994,2020]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">et al</emphasis>
. 2018
</bibRefCitation>
: Art. 36.3).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="DE7D36FEFFAD1223FF59F85B25E0F7B7" blockId="3.[136,1452,914,2093]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107">
Note that these two designations are not illegitimate as stated by 
<bibRefCitation id="BA534B0FFFAD1223FC6AF85A23FFF793" author="Descoings, B." box="[910,1167,2030,2056]" pageId="3" pageNumber="107" pagination="143 - 181" refId="ref3596" refString="Descoings, B. (2003) Kalanchoe. In: U. Eggli (Ed.) Illustrated handbook of succulent plants: Crassulaceae. Springer-Verlag, Berlin &amp; Heidelberg, pp. 143 - 181." type="book chapter" year="2003">Descoings (2003: 148)</bibRefCitation>
. For that to have been the case, they should have been validly published.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
